<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="description" content="">
  <meta name="author" content="">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/icon.png">
  <title><%= @title %> | 2Chez</title>


  <!-- Bootstrap core CSS -->
  <link href="/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <!-- Stylesheet -->
  <link href="<%= @css %>.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <style id="holderjs-style" type="text/css"></style>
</head>
<body style>
  <section class="nav-section">
    <header class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top" role="navigation">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-1">
            <a type="button" class="btn">
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home"></span> Home
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>  
    </header>
  </section>

  <div class="site-wrapper">
    <div class="site-wrapper-inner">
      <section class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-1">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-10">
            <div class="container">
              <h1>Hi, <%= @user.capitalize %>.</h1>
              <form action="/menu" method="post">
                
              </form>
              <p>Instructions go here.</p>
              <% if @menu_items != nil %>
                <% @menu_items.each do |item| %>
                  <article class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-2">
                      <p><%= item.name %> (<%= item.menu %>)</p>  
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                      <p><%= item.description %></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-1">
                      <p>$<%= item.price %></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-1">
                      <button class="btn btn-big btn-warning">edit</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-1">
                      <button class="btn btn-big btn-danger">delete</button>
                    </div>
                  </article>  
                <% end %>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

<!-- 

Goals for this page:

- Be accessible only through a successful login
- Redirect to login page if accessed by non-logged-in user
- Allow admin to create MenuItems
- Display current MenuItems, organized by menu (lunch, dinner, etc.)
- Allow admin to edit existing MenuItem properties
- Allow admin to destroy MenuItems, with confirmation prompt

-->